'''施尔登人'''（{{lang-en|Sherden}} 或 Serden、Shardana）是[[古埃及|古埃及]]与[[烏加里特|烏加里特]]铭文与雕刻中记录的公元[[前2千年|前2千年]]后期横行于[[地中海|地中海]]区域的[[海上民族|海上民族]]的一支，在服饰与武器上与[[非利士人|非利士人]]相近，有些施尔登人还成为了埃及的佣兵。施尔登人常装备[[圆盾|圆盾]]、[[长矛|长矛]]、[[长匕首|长匕首]]等武器，被认为和[[撒丁岛|撒丁岛]]有关<ref>{{cite book |author-link=Robert Drews |last=Drews |first=Robert |year=1993 |title=The End of Bronze Age |publisher=Princeton University Press}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal|last=Cline |first=Eric H. |year=1997 |title=Review of Robert Drews' 'The End of the Bronze Age: Changes in warfare and the catastrophe ca. 1200 B.C.' |url=https://archive.org/details/sim_journal-of-near-eastern-studies_1997-04_56_2/page/127 |journal=Journal of Near Eastern Studies |volume=56 |issue=2 |pages=127-129}}</ref><ref>{{cite book |last=Dickinson |first=Oliver T.P.K. |year=1999 |article=Robert Drews’ theories about the nature of war in the late Bronze Age |editor-first=R. |editor-last=Laffineur |title=Polemos: Le Contexte Guerrier en Egee a l'Age du Bronze |series=Aegaeum |volume=19 |publisher=Universite de Liege |pages=21-25}}</ref>。


